data.description: Update:  New Flooring, New lighting, New paint, Cabinets refinished....Imagine the warmth of the sun and the coolness of the water as you relax in your beautiful pool home located in lovely Punta Gorda, Florida.  Just a few short miles from plenty of soft sand, gentle waves from the Gulf of Mexico, and lots of colorful shells, this home offers a new roof, newer AC, newer appliances, new counter tops. Wow! what a find.  This one is a must see on your list of showings.
